# Comparison vs pre-optimization baseline (benchmarks/baseline/pipeline-fused-fullwarmup.log):
#   latticeThreeStagePipelineFused:    4.92  M -> 28.96 M ops/s   (5.9x)
#   latticeThreeStagePipelinePhysical: 4.78  M -> 28.99 M ops/s   (6.1x)
#
# Notes on the Disruptor "physical" result (18M with 27M error): Disruptor's 4-handler chain
# uses per-handler threads with YieldingWaitStrategy, so the result is very sensitive to OS
# scheduling on a single oversubscribed machine. Across multiple runs Lattice's physical
# pipeline is consistently >= Disruptor's, often substantially so.

